file.content:
openapi: "3.0.1"
info:
  title: "Book API"
  description: "Some description"
  contact:
    name: "John Doe"
    email: "jdoe@localhost"
  license:
    name: "Apache 2.0"
    url: "http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.html"
  version: "1.0.0"
tags:
- name: "book"
  description: "Operations about book"
- name: "foo"
  description: "Some other tag"
paths:
  /books/{id}:
    get:
      summary: "Get a book by its id"
      operationId: "findById"
      parameters:
      - name: "id"
        in: "path"
        description: "id of book to be searched"
        required: true
        schema:
          type: "integer"
          format: "int64"
      responses:
        "200":
          description: "Found the book"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Dto"
        "400":
          description: "Invalid id supplied"
          content:
            '*/*': {}
        "404":
          description: "Book not found"
          content:
            '*/*': {}
components:
  schemas:
    Dto:
      type: "object"
      properties:
        field1:
          type: "string"
        field2:
          type: "number"
          format: "double"
        field3:
          type: "string"
          format: "date-time"
